sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Run Orchestrator
    participant K as K8s Controller
    participant DB as Postgres
    participant OBJ as Object Storage

    O->>K: Launch run job
    K->>DB: sandbox_lease(status=running)
    O->>DB: run_step(status=running)

    Note over K: Node preemption/pod eviction
    K-->>O: pod terminated unexpectedly

    O->>OBJ: fetch latest checkpoint
    O->>DB: mark failed attempt, increment retry
    O->>K: relaunch job with resume context
    K->>DB: sandbox_lease(status=restarted)

    O->>DB: run_step(status=running, attempt+1)
    O->>OBJ: persist new checkpoint
    O->>DB: run_step(status=succeeded)
